data.description: **** Updated listing! **** Improved price! Kitchen upgrades! Fresh paint! Motivated Seller! You will love this cozy, meticulously maintained 1,800 sq ft home.  As you step inside, you're greeted with beautiful hardwood stairs, railings and a view of the upgraded kitchen, clean living room and downstairs fireplace!  Upstairs you will find luxurious carpet throughout, and hardwood in the kitchen.  You will find a sunny living room that flows into the dining area, then into the kitchen that houses brand new granite countertops and updated stainless steel appliances.  A huge 21 ft X 13 ft deck surrounded by a meticulously maintained lawn with a great view that backs to a common area filled with trees for your leisure.  The upper level has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, including french doors to the master suite.  The lower level has a spacious great room with built-in bookshelves, a cozy wood burning fireplace with slate surround, a half bathroom, easy access to laundry and a bonus storage area under the foyer!  The 24 ft oversize garage is perfect for the DIY'er or anyone that likes to tinker with projects. The workshop area has been updated with Ulti-MATE Garage Cabinets, Craftsman workbench, hot and cold hose bibs, heavy duty slat wall that supports removable shelves and hooks, and an electrical transfer switch that all convey to the new owner.  This house is generator ready!  The driveway has been widened for extra parking and you're only minutes from shopping, dining and some of the best schools in Maryland.  Easy access to Liberty Reservoir, downtown Sykesville, MD-32, MD 26, MD-97, I-70 and more!
